    "description": "Inbound Tech Inc. engages in the Multilingual CRM and sales outsourcing businesses in Japan. The company offers multilingual contact center services, including help desk and system monitoring services; multilingual/interpretation solutions, such as telephone, AI video, and three-way interpretations that support inbound foreigners in various situations; and contact center BPO services, as well as specialized sales outsourcing services. It also engages in mobile promotion-related business. The company offers services in Japanese, English, Chinese, Korean, Portuguese, Spanish, Thai, Vietnamese, Russian, French, Tagalog, and Nepali languages. It serves clients across various industries, including multinational corporations, foreign-affiliated companies, and consumer goods and services sectors. The company was formerly known as Brainpress Inc. Inbound Tech Inc. was incorporated in 2015 and is headquartered in Shinjuku, Japan."
